    "description": "Thank you for checking out my first game!<br />\r\n<br />\r\n_What To Expect_<br />\r\nNodrog's Fortress is a Tactics-like Turn-Based/Real-Time Strategy Battler that features elements of Chess and American Football in a Pixel Art JRPG inspired package.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nChoose your Archmage, companions to fight for them, and try your hand playing the newly released Story Mode, Quickmatch Mode locally, or engage in Online PVP in Multiplayer Mode!!!<br />\r\n  <br />\r\nWhatever you decide to do, bring your friends!  Get them ready to battle with up to 4 Player/AI Teams in Versus/Team Versus and Survival Modes Locally and Online.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nCheck out the Tutorial Mode and In-Game Guide for a few tips and tricks :)<br />\r\n<br />\r\n_Developer Note_<br />\r\nI hope you enjoy my game and help me make it better with your feedback!  With your help, we can build an even more epic Fortress in the times to come!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nWelcome to the Battle!",
